  "page": "Bloodroyal",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>Bloodroyal</b> is an ancient title traditionally held by the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Yronwood\" title=\"House Yronwood\">House Yronwood</a>. Prior to <a href=\"/index.php/Nymeria%27s_War\" title=\"Nymeria&#39;s War\">Nymeria's War</a>, the Yronwoods were rulers of an independent kingdom in <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a>, styling themselves <a href=\"/index.php/High_King_of_Dorne\" title=\"High King of Dorne\">High Kings of Dorne</a>, among many other titles.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_kingdoms_of_the_first_men.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_kingdoms_of_the_first_men.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>When the Yronwoods bent the knee to <a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\">House Martell</a>, they were allowed to keep their title of the Bloodroyal.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bloodroyal&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Stone_Way\" title=\"Lord of the Stone Way\">Lord of the Stone Way</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Master_of_the_Green_Hills\" title=\"Master of the Green Hills\">Master of the Green Hills</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Warden_of_the_Stone_Way\" title=\"Warden of the Stone Way\">Warden of the Stone Way</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bloodroyal&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_kingdoms_of_the_first_men.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_kingdoms_of_the_first_men.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Kingdoms of the First Men.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403131538\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.009 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.010 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 100/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8538/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 398/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 148/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 626/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    5.471      1 -total\n 75.16%    4.112      1 Template:Ref\n 48.51%    2.654      1 Template:Ref/core\n 23.41%    1.281      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:15670-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403131538 and revision id 264660\n -->\n",
